	   		<div class="comment-entry"  id="comment-49687">
			
				<p>The powers of genuine interest and listening are amazing.</p>
<p>I wrote an article a while back on how to be a confidant. The big secret to getting people to tell you things is to ask them and then shut up and listen. (Being trustworthy is also important.)</p>
<p>Excellent analysis of good conversation!</p>
	            
	            				
